    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! I've taken great care of it, and it still drives like a dream. If you're looking for a quality car without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power delivery through individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by a recently serviced variable M differential lock. The chassis has undergone critical rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. While the exterior displays minor road wear consistent with its driver-quality status, the mechanicals are sorted: the VANOS system has been overhauled and rod bearing clearances have been addressed. It rides on a tight suspension with refreshed bushings, offering the tactile steering feedback and balanced weight distribution this platform is known for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. Ready for pickup.",
