    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a robust powertrain and a well-preserved interior, it offers a refined driving experience that balances performance with long-term reliability. All mechanical systems have been rigorously inspected to ensure they meet our exacting standards for roadworthiness and safety. A distinguished choice for those seeking quality and value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
