      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep it clean and dependable. If you're looking for a great ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
